data.value: Charming Miramar Aparthotel is a modern property in Alexandria, Egypt, offering spacious, air-conditioned apartments with sea views, private kitchens, and balconies. Located near Miami Beach and Abu Haif Beach, it provides amenities like free Wi-Fi, a garden, a terrace, and wellness facilities, including a sauna and hot tub. The aparthotel caters to families and disabled guests and offers a 24-hour front desk and room service. It is well-connected, with Sidi Gaber Railway Station 7.6 km away and Borg El Arab Airport 59 km away.
